title: Looking for a serious ranked team to become the best in OCE/World.
body: I'm a diamond support main looking to play for a team that has high expectations. My best support is Thresh. My IGN is Joshio. Age: 16. Available to skype and teamspeak. Can play everyday for most hours (obviously when school starts i'll be more constricted but I will still be able to play a few games.) Please add me if looking for a serious support.
